          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "We’re still trying to wrap our heads around how one man is being blamed by police for stealing more than 50 luxury cars, which he then gave to each of his 16 girlfriends. Delhi Police interrogated the man, who confessed to the crimes, admitting he stole the vehicles for his girlfriends and “his own hobbies.” The man, named Robin, has a string of known aliases and we’re assuming quite the toolkit for boosting cars.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
